• Place java files, input file and makefile in the same directory.
• Open the terminal and change directory to where the files are located.
• For the compilation, type: make -f project.mak
• After compilation, hashtagcounter.class, MaxFibonacciHeap.class and Node.class will be generated.
• To execute program for given input file, type: java hashtagcounter inputFilename.txt
• You will see output_file.txt with the output in the working directory.
